==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːtə(r)|-uːtə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{law}} A party to a [[suit]] or [[litigation]].
# One who [[sue]]s, [[petition]]s, [[solicit]]s, or [[entreat]]s; a [[petitioner]].
# One who sues for the hand of a woman in marriage; a [[wooer]]; one who [[court]]s a [[mistress]].
====Translations====
'''wooer'''
*German: [[Freier]] {{m}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To play the suitor; to [[woo]]; to [[make love]].

